Package co.acoustic.mobile.push.sdk.api.attribute

Interface QueuedAttributesClient

All Known Implementing Classes:
QueuedAttributesClientImpl
public interface QueuedAttributesClient
This interface is for the sdk queued attributes client implementation. Queued attributes client will add the task to a queue instead of performing it immediately.
